Kita harus segera mundur.

11
00:01:51,539 --> 00:01:53,209
Garis pertempuran sudah jatuh.

12
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,389
Komandan Pengawas!

13
00:02:09,090 --> 00:02:11,359
Oke, mengerti.

14
